msItem.note:
Confirmation by King Edward the Martyr [975×978]; confirmation by King Æthelred [978×984 or 992×1006];
                                        confirmation by King Cnut [1016×1035]; confirmation by Kind Edward the Confessor, with further confirmation of
                                        land at Fiskerton, Lincolnshire; and grant of judicial privileges for land at Great Easton, Leicestershire;
                                        Fletton, Orton and Alwalton, Huntingdonshire; and Osgodby, Lincolnshire [1061×1066]; and confirmation by King
                                        William I, referring specifically to Cotter, Cotton, Manton, Raventhorpe, Messingham, Cleatham, Hibaldstow,
                                        Walcot-on-Humber and Muskham, Lincolnshire [1066×1067] (Kelly).
